message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it stands for Sound and Music Computing, which is directly related to the topic of the paper. Other likely categories could be cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes a new method for semi-supervised learning, cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with audio tagging and boundary detection, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with temporal compression scale and detection of sound events, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper proposes a new approach for weakly-labeled SED.
